CBRE is excited to present for lease 15 Citiwest Court, Altona North.

Perfectly located with Main Road frontage to Grieve Parade, this inner west property provides excellent access to major arterials including the West Gate Freeway, Princes Freeway & Western Ring Road.

Situated approximately 8km west of the Port of Melbourne, 12km west of the CBD and 20km south of Melbourne International Airport.

15 Citiwest Court boasts the following key features:
+ High clearance warehouse: 7,221sqm*
+ Dual level corporate office and staff amenities: 398sqm*
+ Large heavy-duty hardstand allowing efficient truck flow: 4,016sqm*
+ Total Site Area: 15,189sqm*
+ A-Double, B-Double & Semi-Trailer combination vehicle access
+ Truck ingress via Citiwest Court & Egress via Grieve Parade
+ Main Road frontage allowing excellent signage opportunities
+ Separate car and truck entry/exit
+ K17 ESFR sprinkler system
+ Great internal clearance (12.2m)
+ 7T Racking post loads
+ Ample on-site car parking (50 bays)
+ Immediate access to West Gate Freeway via Grieve Parade

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the listed CBRE agents.

*approximate

CBRE is pleased to present 30-68 Taras Avenue, Altona North, for lease. 

This highly functional office/warehouse facility is strategically positioned within the highly sought after industrial and logistics precinct of Altona North, approximately 9kms west of the Port of Melbourne and 12kms west of Melbourne's CBD.

The property has excellent connections to the surrounding major arterial road networks including the Princes Freeway, West Gate Freeway and Western Ring Road.

30-68 Taras Avenue offers the following features;
+   Total gross lettable area (GLA): 40,831sqm*
+   Ability to Lease as smaller areas from 10,000sqm*
+   Corporate office and staff amenities: 2,949sqm*
+   Mezzanine storage area: 4,693sqm*
+   Extremely functional high clearance warehouse
+   Existing racking to remain
+   Complete drive around truck access
+   True transport facility with ample truck manoeuvrability and parking
+   Substantial hardstand
+   Multiple canopies
+   Multiple on-grade roller shutter doors and recessed docks
+   Separate car and truck access with ample on-site car parking
+   ESFR sprinkler system
+   Modern amenities throughout

For further information, please contact the appointed CBRE agents.

*approx.
